<!-- BLOCK 16. Bybit FAQ -->
<div class="p2-section">
  <div class="p2-inner">
    <h2 class="p2-h2">{exchange.name} Referral Code — FAQ</h2>
    <div class="p2-faq">
      <details class="p2-faq-item">
        <summary class="p2-faq-q">Do I have to make a cryptocurrency deposit?</summary>
        <div class="p2-faq-a">Not for every task. KYC verification alone may unlock a small reward in the welcome package. However, the larger deposit bonus and most milestone rewards do require you to fund your account. The exact deposit threshold for each tier is shown on the official {exchange.name} bonus page after you register.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="p2-faq-item">
        <summary class="p2-faq-q">Can I get more than one {exchange.name} bonus?</summary>
        <div class="p2-faq-a">Within the welcome package, yes — each completed task unlocks its own reward. You can earn multiple rewards by completing KYC, making a first deposit, placing a futures trade, and meeting volume milestones. The welcome package itself is a one-time offer for new accounts and cannot be repeated on the same account.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="p2-faq-item">
        <summary class="p2-faq-q">What are the {exchange.name} fees?</summary>
        <div class="p2-faq-a">{exchange.name}'s standard spot trading fee is {exchange.fees.spot.maker} for both makers and takers. Perpetual futures fees are {exchange.fees.futures.maker} for makers and {exchange.fees.futures.taker} for takers. Options are {exchange.fees.options.maker} maker and {exchange.fees.options.taker} taker. Some welcome package rewards include a fee discount voucher — check the Rewards Hub after registering to see whether one is available for your account.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="p2-faq-item">
        <summary class="p2-faq-q">Which currency are rewards paid in?</summary>
        <div class="p2-faq-a">Most {exchange.name} welcome bonus rewards are denominated in USDT or issued as USDT-equivalent trading vouchers. Some rewards come as experience points (EXP) that convert to USDT after you meet a trading volume requirement. Specific reward currencies are shown for each task inside the {exchange.name} welcome offer page.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="p2-faq-item">
        <summary class="p2-faq-q">Can existing users use the referral code?</summary>
        <div class="p2-faq-a">No. The {exchange.name} referral code {offer.promoCode} is for new users only and must be entered during account creation. It cannot be added to an existing {exchange.name} account after registration. If you already have a {exchange.name} account, check the ongoing Rewards Hub inside your account instead.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="p2-faq-item">
        <summary class="p2-faq-q">Is the {exchange.name} bonus available in every country?</summary>
        <div class="p2-faq-a">No. {exchange.name} restricts access in a number of jurisdictions, including the United States, United Kingdom, and Canada. Even in countries where {exchange.name} is available, specific bonus tasks or reward amounts may differ by region. After registering, the official {exchange.name} bonus page will show which welcome tasks are active for your account and location.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="p2-faq-item">
        <summary class="p2-faq-q">Why isn't the referral code working?</summary>
        <div class="p2-faq-a">Referral codes must be entered during the account creation step — they cannot be applied to an account that already exists. If you are registering for the first time and the code is not accepted, check that you are using the correct code (<strong>{offer.promoCode}</strong>), that you are accessing the sign-up form via the official {exchange.name} link, and that your country is not in the restricted list. If the problem persists, contact {exchange.name} support through live chat.</div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

